    "I. INTRODUCTIONAI/ML models are widely used in scientific research.",
    "Their traceability (where and in what manner used, how one AI/ML model is related to another, etc) is often overlooked.",
    "But for responsible use of AI and to increase the reproducibility of science, this traceability is important.",
    "AI/ML model cards are a step in the right direction.An AI/ML Model Card is a structured overview of how an AI/ML model was designed and evaluated.",
    "Mitchell et al."
